      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1050 - Muawiya ibn Maysara narrated from  Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as): \"Can a person pray while sitting in the position of tawarruk (cross-legged) or with his legs spread out?\"\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in that.\""
        ]
